data.description: Introducing this charming brick home with vaulted ceilings, ideally situated on a spacious corner lot. The heart of this home is the stunning kitchen featuring a stylish island. Enjoy ample natural light and energy savings with solar panels and a battery backup system. Step outside to a large yard, perfect for outdoor gatherings. A perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm awaits you in this must-see property!
